Third-party component: Konclude OWL-DL Reasoning Kernel
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The file dist/konclude.wasm is compiled from the Konclude reasoning kernel,
which is copyright (c) University of Ulm and released under the GNU Lesser
General Public License v3.0 (LGPLv3).

  Steigmiller, A., Liebig, T., & Glimm, B. (2014).
  Konclude: System Description.
  Journal of Web Semantics, 27–28, 78–85. doi:10.1016/j.websem.2014.06.003

As required by LGPLv3 §4, the complete Konclude source with all applied
modifications is available at:

  https://github.com/ThHanke/rdf-reasoner-konclude

Clone with --recurse-submodules to obtain vendor/konclude/ (the Konclude source)
and patches/ (every modification applied to it). To recompile the WASM binary:

  git clone --recurse-submodules https://github.com/ThHanke/rdf-reasoner-konclude
  docker compose run --rm build

